### ============================================================================
### Web Search Endpoints
### ============================================================================

### General web search
POST http://localhost:8000/web-search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "latest technology trends",
  "categories": "general",
  "language": "en",
  "time_range": "week",
  "page": 1,
  "per_page": 10
}

### Web search with bang syntax
POST http://localhost:8000/web-search/bang
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "economy",
  "bang": "!yhn",
  "language": "en",
  "time_range": "month",
  "page": 1,
  "per_page": 20
}

### Get available bang shortcuts
GET http://localhost:8000/web-search/bangs

### Web search with markdown conversion (save to file)
POST http://localhost:8000/web-search/markdown
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "artificial intelligence news",
  "categories": "news",
  "language": "en",
  "time_range": "week",
  "page": 1,
  "per_page": 10,
  "max_conversions": 5,
  "export_to_file": true
}

### Web search with markdown conversion (memory only)
POST http://localhost:8000/web-search/markdown
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "artificial intelligence news",
  "categories": "news",
  "language": "en",
  "time_range": "week",
  "page": 1,
  "per_page": 10,
  "max_conversions": 5,
  "export_to_file": false
}


